Here's your complete full-stack LLM Gateway. Here's what was built:

рџ“Ѓ What's Inside
backend/main.py вЂ” FastAPI
SSE streaming via StreamingResponse with async generators for both OpenAI and Anthropic SDKs
Prompt router вЂ” inspects the model field and dispatches to the correct provider automatically
Token bucket rate limiter вЂ” 20 req/min per IP, returns 429 with Retry-After header
Usage tracker вЂ” records prompt/completion tokens per request, exposed via GET /usage
Graceful error handling вЂ” catches RateLimitError from both SDKs and emits SSE error events
frontend/LLMDashboard.jsx вЂ” React
useSSEChat hook вЂ” handles fetch() with ReadableStream, parses SSE events, and appends tokens live
Stop button вЂ” uses AbortController to cancel in-flight streams
Model switcher вЂ” color-coded by provider (green = OpenAI, amber = Anthropic)
Settings panel вЂ” system prompt, temperature slider, max tokens slider
Analytics panel вЂ” fetches /usage and shows per-provider request/token breakdown
Token usage bar вЂ” shows prompt vs. completion token split after each response
